Description: English-like programming language that transpiles to Python
 Ethos lets you write code in plain English syntax with no brackets
 or semicolons. Every statement ends with a period. Supports if/while
 loops, functions, imports, type casting, string slicing, and Traits
 (both Python packages and native C/C++/Rust binaries via ctypes).
 This Termux build runs on Python via zipapp with no native deps.
